jab humay commonjs ko ecmascript pe convert karna hota hai to is tarah se tsconfig or package.json ki setting karni hoti hai pher apki
ts wali file compile Ecmascript pe hoge instead of common js. is setting ko karne se run time pe error b chale jaengy.
 
 
TSCONFIG SETTING From COMMON JS to ECMASCRIPT.

  "target": "ESNext",    
 "module": "ESNext", 

PACKAGE.JSON SETTING from COMMON & ECMASCRIPT to run time error.

  "type": "module",
  
  .
